      Microsoft, NVIDIA, and Palo Alto Networks. Its defenders-first
      posture is the spiritual model for this lane's isolation contract
      (CLAUDE.md §1), cloud-LLM-key-leak pre-commit hooks, and
      freeze-verify-on-every-commit discipline. The user's agent-team
      playbook at prism42/.claude/skills/glasswing-discipline/ is named
      in tribute, sharing the butterfly metaphor (Greta oto's
      transparent wings).

